{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "tomodachi-petshop-api",
    "name": "Tomodachi Pet Shop API",
    "description": "API Collection untuk Tomodachi Pet Shop Management System\n\n**Base URL:** http://127.0.0.1:8000\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Login terlebih dahulu untuk mendapatkan token\n2. Token akan tersimpan otomatis di environment variable\n3. Gunakan environment: \"Local Development\"",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "26906715"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Authentication",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Get Captcha (LAKUKAN DULU)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (jsonData.data) {",
                  "        pm.environment.set('captcha_key', jsonData.data.captcha_key);",
                  "        console.log('✅ Captcha Key: ' + jsonData.data.captcha_key);",
                  "        console.log('❓ Question: ' + jsonData.data.question);",
                  "        console.log('💡 Jawab pertanyaan di atas, lalu masukkan jawaban di Login request');",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/captcha",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "captcha"]
            },
            "description": "📌 STEP 1: Dapatkan CAPTCHA terlebih dahulu\n\n⚠️ PENTING:\n1. Click SEND\n2. Lihat Console (bawah kiri) - akan ada pertanyaan soal penjumlahan\n3. Jawab soal tersebut, misalnya 3 + 5 = 8\n4. Copy jawaban, lalu buka request 'Login'\n5. Paste jawaban di field 'captcha_answer' pada Login request"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Login (SETELAH GET CAPTCHA)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (jsonData.data && jsonData.data.token) {",
                  "        pm.environment.set('token', jsonData.data.token);",
                  "        console.log('✅ Login Berhasil!');",
                  "        console.log('🔑 Token: ' + jsonData.data.token);",
                  "        console.log('👤 User: ' + jsonData.data.user.name + ' (' + jsonData.data.user.role.name + ')');",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"owner@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"password\",\n  \"captcha_key\": \"{{captcha_key}}\",\n  \"captcha_answer\": \"GANTI_DENGAN_JAWABAN_SOAL_DARI_CAPTCHA\",\n  \"remember_me\": false\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "📌 STEP 2: Login dengan Captcha\n\n⚠️ PENTING:\n1. Sebelum click SEND, buka request 'Get Captcha' dulu\n2. Copy jawaban dari console (misal: 8)\n3. Paste ke field 'captcha_answer' di bawah\n4. Klik SEND\n5. Token akan tersimpan otomatis!"
          },
          "response": []
        },
